annotations.description: A Classic Champagne Cocktail named after a storied century old lodging in downtown Louisville Kentucky? Or A Fake? The Seelbach cocktail was created by a bar...
annotations.title: The Strange But True Story of The Seelbach Cocktail, is it modern or classic?

textContent:
1oz (30ml) Bourbon
.5oz (15ml) Cointreau
2 Dashes Angostura Bitters
2 Dashes Peychauds Bitters
Top Prosecco 
Orange Twist Garnish

Build in champagne glass
